ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Nursing 917 was an excellent guided, hands-on, immersion into advanced statistics. Classes consisted of a combination of lecture and lab, this was a very useful way to learn. I walked away with valuable knowledge that I can actually use. This was the most useful statistics class I have ever taken. I would highly recommend taking this class with Dr. Holland.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: This course helped me to know the most commonly used statistical method in nursing research, thus help me to make informed choices on statistical methods for my dissertation in the future.
This course provided me with knowledge useful for study design and analysis.
